# Task T-020@20260427T001208Z: Add `generated_content_dominance` antipattern detector to `render/antipatterns.py`.

## Acceptance Criteria

- Per-piece check: fires when `samples_by_source["generated"] / total_sampler_events > 0.3`<br/>- Rolling-window check: fires when above ratio holds for 7 consecutive days of the last 50 pieces<br/>- Detector returns warning per-piece; rolling violation upgrades to MUST FIX<br/>- Tests with synthetic piece histories cover both thresholds

**Tier:** T1

